  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once per day, you can issue an order as per @Compendium[pf1.spells.zqj5qzyl46af27v0]{Suggestion}. Any creature of chaotic alignment has difficulty defying your command, taking a –4 penalty on its saving throw to resist it.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, your command function as per @Compendium[pf1.spells.52v3fogun1n9jzum]{Suggestion, Mass}. If you are wearing Hellknight plate or a signifer mask, your command’s target takes an additional –2 penalty on its saving throw to resist the order (regardless of the target’s alignment; this stacks with the penalty chaotic creatures take).</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level to select this revelation.</p>"
    },
